examples.title: Build and manage a resilient service using an &AWS; SDK
examples.title_abbrev: Build and manage a resilient service
examples.synopsis: create a load-balanced web service that returns book, movie, and song recommendations. The example shows how the service responds to failures, and how to restructure the service for more resilience when failures occur.
